latestPosts.caption:
To My Wonderful Family and friends,

From the bottom of my heart THANK YOU 🧿.
I never imagined feeling the way I did this year: overwhelmed, in the best way, by love, laughter, and joy.

You all turned something I once disliked into one of the most beautiful memories of my life. The surprise, the décor, the thoughtfulness behind every detail, and most of all the warmth and presence of each of you… it was magic.

I felt truly seen, celebrated, and deeply loved. You changed my mind about birthdays not with grand gestures, but with genuine care and love and effort . You reminded me that it’s not about the day itself, but about the people who make it special.

Thank you for making me feel so incredibly lucky. I’ll cherish this forever.

I love you insane amounts 💗
Thank you so much for everything 🥹🥳

latestPosts.caption: Happyyyy birthdayyy myyyyy saviourrrrr loveeeee youuu alotttttt💗✨🧿

Happy Birthday Papa💗

No words can truly capture how much you mean to me. You’ve been my strength, my guide, and my quiet hero. Even in the moments I couldn’t say it out loud, I’ve always admired your sacrifices, your wisdom, and the love you gave without ever asking for anything in return.

Today, I just want to say thank you for everything. I’m proud to be your child, and I hope I can make you proud too.
Wishing you a birthday filled with peace, love, and all the happiness you deserve. I love you, insane amounts 

Forever your little girl 💗
